name: Williams Joy
description:
Remember a 90’s tv ad where a couple are walking out of a Black-tie affair when she touches his arm and barely nods toward a playground across the street. The next scene he’s pushing her on the swing still wearing their formals. That’s me. Playful: sophisticated yet determined to cherish the child within. Independent: yet caring and an intuitive communicator. Emotionally mature: goal-oriented yet spontaneous, romantic yet realistic. Seemingly balanced- yin and yang, prompting some to regard me as an enigma (or, at least, very confused).
What I seek is a fellow gourmet to share all food fun with. If you don’t appreciate fine dining and ethnic eateries, click, “next” now.
I love to laugh, being romantic, kind and tender. I am honest, fun and almost single. I am a simple fun Loving girl”. I am sweet and down to earth, real and open to a relationship. I am optimistic, fun and goal oriented.
I like to have night walks on the beach in the moon light. I’m caring, loyal, passionate and beautiful. I love smiling and laughing and having a great time.I love to cook,camp,hike,etc.. I am independent, and ready to have fun with the right Guy. If you like what you’ve read shoot me an email
